snippet.title: BattleSky Brigade Trailer - Pillage, Plunder, PEWPEW!
snippet.description:
BattleSky Brigade is a mobile RTS with social elements. Form alliances and defend your Guild Heart against would-be invaders in the Wyldes. Pillage, plunder, and PEWPEW!

Check it out at www.battleskybrigade.com
Instagram: battleskybrigade
Twitter: battleskybrig
